Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS部隊 出動准備
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS部隊 出動准備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能乘座Ahead了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部機能 沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN-DRIVE 連接開始
