Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要戰斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ahead第1小隊 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勒維機 TAKE OFF
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體的整備萬無一失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的奧義什麼的部分也更進了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毋須多言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了然於心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光學攝像頭捕捉到MS部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離戰斗宙域還有0054
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 不好了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人來了的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之像往常一樣拜托大家了的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 簡略過頭了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 肩膀的狀況如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的MS部隊 捕捉到總計12架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要輕敵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方部隊裡有變革者的專用機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·庫洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS部隊裡 有露易絲所乘的機體在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這4個月來 為了整頓戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直躲著敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 已經要決戰了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對露易絲出手麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就要看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗 不僅僅是指去破壞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去創造什麼 也是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的Gundam的話是能夠做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 就看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 無法扣下扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了對著露易絲不斷叫喊之外什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去見她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去見露易絲·哈勒維
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1 第2 第3艙門 打開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德先生 期待你的戰果的說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee 提艾利亞·愛德 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准備好了麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以 給我出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會守護你的哦 瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer-Arios 阿雷魯亞·哈普狄斯姆 索瑪·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入迎擊行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐 在聽麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是彈無虛發啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說 什麼時候開始的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛之花滿開的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒… 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯 彈無虛發喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去見她吧 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 走吧 剎那!
