Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務 開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯 快逃! 保安局的家伙們…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱尼!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險 來這邊!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上孩子們快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 約瑟夫!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份情報一定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要由你直接傳達給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.93,0:23:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個坐標 就是維塔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:60.57,0:24:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰場上閃耀著的TRANS-AM Raiser 的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓擦肩而過的兩人終於對面重逢
